Name: Average resolution time following 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Accepted' state activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Maximum time gap observed between 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the next activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases that also contain 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer occurs

Name: Total time spent in 'Unmatched + Unmatched' across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the first 'Completed' state activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest single instance of 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest single instance of 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with more than one instance of this activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average time between consecutive 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Time from the first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the last 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases that transition to 'Completed + In Call' within three activities afterwards
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the top 10 longest cases
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the top 10 shortest cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'
